{"data": [{"id": "4747458", "title": "Royal Caribbean Cruises: Why You Should Disembark", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Royal Caribbean, Navigator of the Seas cruise ship and tender boat\" data-id=\"1712186363\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sanfel/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>I give Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RCL\" title=\"Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd.\">RCL</a></span>) a sell rating because the company has poor short-term liquidity, a massive amount of long-term debt, and is overvalued by 227% from its current intrinsic value of $70.48, much of which is due to the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747458-royal-caribbean-cruises-why-you-should-disembark", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 15:38:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747353", "title": "TKO Group: WWE Evolution Continues With Netflix Shift", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"WWE World Wrestling Entertainment American professional fake wrestling promotion company headquarters in Stamford Connecticut.\" data-id=\"2163043433\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1068px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(6