ty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">BlackRock's corporate headquarters in New York City, New York.</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">georgeclerk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>For me, my dividend growth investing strategy is simple. I aim to own the most dominant players in massive and growing industries. This is because industry dominance is usually reflective of companies</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747457-blackrock-now-is-not-the-time-to-buy-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 15:25:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747456", "title": "PUTW: Solid Way To Add Flexibility To A Portfolio", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female yoga student doing pose in yoga studio\" data-id=\"2155324534\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seeki