ot intended</em></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291620275/image_1291620275.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747379-my-portfolios-roadmap-for-thriving-in-2025s-economic-crossroads", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 15:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747460", "title": "The Rules Of Bob Farrell - An Updated Illustrated Guide", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200758333/image_1200758333.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Looking, 3d render\" data-id=\"1200758333\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5914px\" height=\"3424px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200758333/image_1200758333.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200758333/image_1200758333.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200758333/image_1200758333.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200758333/image_1200758333.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200758333/image_1200758333.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200758333/image_1200758333.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200758333/image_1200758333.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200758333/image_1200758333.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Sezeryadigar</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In a recent discussion on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nASrF7t64kY\" rel=\"noopener noopener noopener noopener\"><strong>TheRealInvestmentShow</strong></a>, Bob Farrell and his 10 investment rules were discussed, which elicited several email questions asking, <em>\"Who is Bob Farrell, and where are these rules?\"</em>. I often forget how old I have become, and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200758333/image_1200758333.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747460-rules-of-bob-farrell-updated-illustrated-guide", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 14:55:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747451", "title": "Safe Bulkers: Safe Route To Financial Stability Despite Headwinds", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1064904328/image_1064904328.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"General cargo ship at sea - Aerial image\" data-id=\"1064904328\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1064904328/image_1064904328.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1064904328/image_1064904328.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1064904328/image_1064904328.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1064904328/image_1064904328.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1064904328/image_1064904328.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1064904328/image_1064904328.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1064904328/image_1064904328.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1064904328/image_1064904328.jpg?io=getty-